Package pygar.zoneable

Class ClientProfile

java.lang.Object
pygar.configuration.Profile
pygar.zoneable.ClientProfile
public class ClientProfile
extends Profile
This subclass extends the Profile with encryption operations that are used only by the innermost zone of client applications and never in the blind-agent server. For the moment it is only a placeholder that does nothing. Needs work!!
